PageInfo.Message:
In addition to basic attacks, players can use
<COL ffdc78>Custom Skills</COL> by consuming
Stamina.
<PADM> Press <KC WEAPON_SUB> and <KC ATTACK1>/<KC
ATTACK2> together.
Press <KC WEAPON_MAIN> and <KC ATTACK1>/<KC
ATTACK2> together.
<KEYM> Press <KC SKILL_CUSTOM3> <KC SKILL_CUSTOM4>
Press <KC SKILL_CUSTOM1> <KC SKILL_CUSTOM2>
</KEYM>
Check the guide in the bottom right of the screen
to see what kind of techniques can be used.

Depending on the job, the available custom skills
may vary. Please try them out during combat.
Please note that the custom skills set during the
introductory quest "Resolutions and Omens" are
temporary and exclusive to that quest.
